1
00:00:02,172 --> 00:00:04,511
iz in Mezritsh?

2
00:00:04,180 --> 00:00:08,848
yo. ikh kum keyn Mezritsh, alzo m'veyst nisht vos tsu tun,

3
00:00:08,888 --> 00:00:20,323
un ikh iz iz a yidish kind un s'do zeyer fil iz gevezn dezertirn un azelkhe vos zenen bafrayt gevorn fun der rusisher armey.

4
00:00:20,447 --> 00:00:24,325
s'shoyn do hundert tsvontsik yidn, un s'do a beker a beker oykhet.

5
00:00:24,325 --> 00:00:33,212
un ale ge- ikh hob gehat opgenu- un ikh hob ge- ikh bin geven nisht, gut sheyn ongetun un yung oykhet. un ikh hob zikh shoyn ge- mit dem ZUREK, mit di zup fun di

6
00:00:33,212 --> 00:00:36,509
fun der poyer, bin ikh sh- hob ikh shoyn gut oysgezen.

7
00:00:36,509 --> 00:00:42,463
vi nor a man, azoy fil mener. di varsheverin, di varsheverin, di varshever, di varshever.

8
00:00:42,790 --> 00:00:50,152
a klal, ikh bin gevezn epes a por teg, mitn kind, dos kind hot zikh ongehoybn popraven oykhet.

9
00:00:50,152 --> 00:00:54,776
s'dokh geven a koysh mit beyner, mamesh oyf tsu shtarbn, tsvelef kilo hot zi gevoygn

10
00:00:54,776 --> 00:00:58,210
ven ikh hob ir opgenumen nokh a por yor zayn dortn bay im.

11
00:00:58,210 --> 00:01:04,451
vayl zi hot nisht gekent lebn im. im hot zi lib gehat. er iz dokh geven a kultureler mentsh, er hot dokh ir gelernt.

12
00:01:04,608 --> 00:01:12,838
un er un er hot un er hot gezen az a fakt az zi hot ongehoybn geyn in shule bald az er iz gekumen, in der driter klas.

13
00:01:14,582 --> 00:01:19,234
ikh bin do a por tog, un ikh trakht mikh, ikh darf dokh makhn epes a lebn.

14
00:01:20,826 --> 00:01:25,832
un ikh gey ikh for tsurik keyn Paplovits nemen a por zakhn vos ikh hob shoyn gehat.

15
00:01:26,344 --> 00:01:32,998
ikh zol epes hobn zikh vi tsu dos. in komitet hot men mir gezogt bald, in ershtn tog ven ikh bin gekumen,

16
00:01:32,998 --> 00:01:39,264
az m'zukht a shnayderin in MINISTERSTWO vu s'geven a mol fun fun der ban,

17
00:01:39,321 --> 00:01:42,397
iz haynt do kh- a kikh,

18
00:01:42,397 --> 00:01:48,832
un m'firt a shnayderay vayl ale alerley zenen opgerisn opgeshlisn, di vos zenen geven in Rusland, un di vos zenen in Poyln,

19
00:01:48,832 --> 00:01:52,981
m'darf zey epes oyfneyen, afilek der prezident, di PREZYDENTOWA.

20
00:01:53,028 --> 00:01:55,869
nor s'arbetn tsvelef shikses,

21
00:01:56,314 --> 00:02:01,860
un zey kumen der porutshnik, mit a range heyst es, a militer man, vos firt dos on dos,

22
00:02:02,220 --> 00:02:08,542
er er vil a yidishe zol hobn an oyg oyf di shikses. zey hobn nisht gehat keyn tsutroy. farshteyt?

23
00:02:09,088 --> 00:02:12,592
alzo, ikh hob shoyn gevust az ikh hob shoyn vu tsu geyn arbetn oykhet.

24
00:02:12,885 --> 00:02:20,827
bin ikh hob ikh genumen un bin avekgeforn tsurik nemen ale zakhn dortn fun Pabovits vos ikh hob nokh dem gantsn vinter opgearbet.

25
00:02:22,099 --> 00:02:30,795
un un zog ikh un ts- oyf tsurik vegs, vel ikh mikh heysn, hob ikh shoyn gehat a a oyfn veg gekhapt azan a taksi, an oyto,

26
00:02:30,795 --> 00:02:35,340
aza mine s'iz an oyto geven, a vegele, alnfals a shtikl mashin.

27
00:02:35,346 --> 00:02:38,228
un heyst mikh opshteln vu s'heybt zikh on Vlokhi.

28
00:02:38,228 --> 00:02:43,119
zog ikh yetst vel ikh tsugeyn zen vos mit di shtub iz. s'dokh an eygntum.

29
00:02:43,193 --> 00:02:46,480
tsi s'vet epes zayn derfun. ikh ho- ikh hob dokh shoyn gornisht gehat,

30
00:02:46,480 --> 00:02:50,476
gornisht farmogt. epes a a kishele hob ikh shoyn gehat, ikh hob es alts genumen.

31
00:02:51,023 --> 00:02:59,061
un ikh gey oyf mayn rikhtikn veg. forn ale shofern, shiker, ale rusn,

32
00:02:59,061 --> 00:03:04,028
nisht zey hobn nisht keyn spirtn, nor zey trinken alkohol, un bren-spirt,

33
00:03:04,371 --> 00:03:10,755
un ikh gey oyf mayn veg, un ikh krig a un un ikh fil az er fort oyf mir on,

34
00:03:10,755 --> 00:03:16,116
un ikh krig epes do a klap, ikh farlir nisht UNK vos in kop arayn nisht, un ikh tsu mikh azoy tsunoyf,

35
00:03:16,116 --> 00:03:22,073
un s'get mikh a fir ariber der tsenter vogn, a Shrudebek iz dos geven, an amerikaner last-oyto.

36
00:03:22,292 --> 00:03:25,728
vos zey hobn di r- di amerikaner hobn gegebn far di rusn oykhet.

37
00:03:26,325 --> 00:03:32,481
un azoy iz geven ze- a shpitol dortn in Vlokhi, bloyz fun di SAMOCHODn.

38
00:03:32,481 --> 00:03:35,882
azoy vi haynt bay undz, a aza min oys shekhteray.

39
00:03:36,329 --> 00:03:40,207
alzo, s'kumt on a por goyim, m'firt mikh un m'nemt mikh in shpitol arayn.

40
00:03:40,298 --> 00:03:45,809
un ikh lig op tsvey vokhn un di Sheymels vu dos kind iz veyst nisht vu ikh bin ahingekumen.

41
00:03:47,537 --> 00:03:55,108
nisht ikh, ikh bin gelegn mit dem fus, nisht tsebrokhn gevorn. nor der fus iz geven shvarts, s'geven oysgegosn dos blut.

42
00:03:55,300 --> 00:04:03,557
iz bin ikh gelegn tsvey vokhn azoy nokh nokh ale tsores, mitn fus azoy tsum sufit, mit aza ekstere eksperiment,

43
00:04:03,557 --> 00:04:09,252
un di hant, un do bloyz der oyf der f- nogl, der di der nogl iz aropgefaln.

44
00:04:09,252 --> 00:04:18,193
do hob ikh gekrign mit dem letstn rod, vayl ikh hob mikh azoy tsunoyf gekortshet, ikh hob nisht farloyrn. der vogn iz adurkhgeforn, dos letste, der letster rod iz aroyf oyf mir.

45
00:04:19,414 --> 00:04:28,672
dernokhn, ikh bin aroys, bin ikh shoyn gegangen glaykh oyf mayn veg, yo, in komitet arayn, u- u- u- ts- nokhn kind,

46
00:04:28,797 --> 00:04:36,266
un ikh hob gezogt in komitet az ikh ken nokh dervayl nisht, ikh muz opnemen dos kind, dos kind tsum ersht aynordenen. zogn zey, dos kind e'mir undz tsunemen.

47
00:04:36,559 --> 00:04:42,723
s'iz do a kinder-hoyz in Otvotsk. dort iz gevezn a a linye vos m'iz geforn

48
00:04:42,723 --> 00:04:44,352
UNK,

49
00:04:44,352 --> 00:04:48,520
nor in yener tsayt hobn zey geshafn kinder-hayzer far di vos zey hobn opgenumen fun di

50
00:04:48,520 --> 00:04:53,542
vos zey hobn gefunen in di gasn oder opgenumen bay goyim. der komitet, der yidisher komitet.

51
00:04:53,566 --> 00:04:57,444
shoyn. un ikh ikh gey ir opnemen,

52
00:04:57,653 --> 00:05:06,779
iz dem tog vos s'geshen dos hot zi zikh oyfgekhapt, zi hot mir dernokh dertseylt, zi hot gevoynt zi do gekumen. zey hobn gevoynt in Belgye dernokhn.

53
00:05:06,779 --> 00:05:10,236
zeyer raykhe mentshn, un zenen zey geven.

54
00:05:10,309 --> 00:05:14,972
zey lebn zi lebt shoyn nisht, zi lebt shoyn oykh zikher nisht. er iz geshtorbn shoyn do oykhet.

55
00:05:14,972 --> 00:05:19,494
nor demolts hot zi mir dertseylt, az dem tog vos mir iz dos geshen, di nakht,

56
00:05:19,494 --> 00:05:22,942
hot zi zikh oyfgekhapt, UNK.

57
00:05:22,982 --> 00:05:25,355
dos heyst, ikh hob shoyn nisht keyn mamen oykhet.

58
00:05:25,362 --> 00:05:27,713
dem tatn hot zi gevust er iz umgekumen.

59
00:05:27,673 --> 00:05:28,916
dos kind.

60
00:05:27,713 --> 00:05:28,883
fun dem goy.

61
00:05:30,390 --> 00:05:36,948
fun di goy, oder zi hot gehert politik, oder m'hot geleyent a tsaytung, ikh veys nisht vos, zi hot dokh gehat farshtand oysergeveyntlekh.

62
00:05:32,162 --> 00:05:33,320
ir hot mikh,

63
00:05:38,052 --> 00:05:41,860
a klal ikh lo- ikh kum tsu geyn un vil nemen dos kind,

64
00:05:43,283 --> 00:05:50,923
zogt er, zogt mir dos meydl, dos yidishe vos m'hot shoyn opgenumen fun di goyim, vos zi hot getun alts in shtub, gekokht un gevashn un alding,

65
00:05:50,923 --> 00:05:57,200
in di shtub iz geven an araynfor hoyz. ver s'iz gekumen, fun velkher zayt, iz gegangen tsu di Sheymels.

66
00:05:57,947 --> 00:06:06,277
vayl zey hobn keynem nisht gehat, zey hobn gehat tsvey zin, zenen zey umgekumen in poylishn oyfshtand in Varshe. un zey hobn oykhet ibergelebt in Varshe ergets in a bunker.

67
00:06:06,672 --> 00:06:12,943
AI- I- HAIKAR, ikh vil nemen dos kind un geb aza rir on,

68
00:06:13,185 --> 00:06:20,249
ikh fil az s'hot fil nis, zog ikh vi azoy fir ikh ir avek in dem hoyz arayn? m'vet dokh ir opshern di hor!

69
00:06:20,796 --> 00:06:22,984
yo, in komitet hot men mir gezogt,

70
00:06:23,108 --> 00:06:32,467
az ale kinder zenen opgeshoyrn vayl m'hot genumen kinder fun gas, farloyzte, farbrudikte, un un s'nokh s'epes do a krankeyt oykhet dortn.

71
00:06:32,878 --> 00:06:35,116
un ikh hob n- do hob ikh nisht vu tsu geyn.

72
00:06:35,140 --> 00:06:42,823
ikh hob nisht vu ikh hob ni- ikh hob nisht keyn shtub, ikh hob nisht vu tsu geyn. tsu dem Noyekhn vos hot gevolt mikh arayn farbetn oyf der SAPA, vel ikh dokh nisht geyn,

73
00:06:42,823 --> 00:06:49,849
trots dem vos s'volt geven der rikhtikster plats, a khaver, vos ken, un veyst az dos kind iz do bay Brovlevski.

74
00:06:49,939 --> 00:06:53,994
nor er iz a biterer mentsh gevezn. zog ikh, tsu im gey ikh nisht.

75
00:06:53,994 --> 00:07:03,298
un nem dos kind, un gey aroyf tsu di tsu der tsu dem Droshn on dem fus vos ikh bin gevezn,

76
00:07:03,304 --> 00:07:10,402
er zi iz geven rikhtik oyf Stolanski nisht vayt, Stolanski tsen hot er gevoynt. azoy vi yetst gedenk ikh es.

77
00:07:11,016 --> 00:07:16,426
un ikh ikh geb ir finef hundert zlotes fun di tsvey toyznt vos ikh hob gekrign fun komitet,

78
00:07:16,888 --> 00:07:21,320
un ikh koyf tsukerlekh, ikh koyf vos es lozt zikh, un leyg avek dos kind,

79
00:07:21,462 --> 00:07:27,176
un do krig azelkhe blozn. un tsip aroys di nis. fun lange hor.

80
00:07:28,313 --> 00:07:32,205
tsvey vokhn hot zikh nisht gelozt vashn, bay di Sheymels.

81
00:07:32,329 --> 00:07:38,021
UNK zi hot shoyn nisht keyn mamen oykhet. a shvere tip dos kind. fun kind vos ⟨oyf? shver.

82
00:07:38,021 --> 00:07:42,110
zi iz f- iber iber dem farshtand shtendik geven antviklt.

83
00:07:42,252 --> 00:07:46,583
zi hot zikh nisht gelozt vashn, zi hot shoyn nisht nokh vos tsu lebn, zi hot shoyn nisht keyn mame.

84
00:07:47,584 --> 00:07:55,065
hobn zey ir nisht gevashn, zey hobn zikh nisht gevolt mit dem arum krign oder shlogn es oder vos. zi hot zikh nisht gelozt vashn. hobn zey farlozt dem kop,

85
00:07:55,065 --> 00:07:59,537
hot zi gehat a kop mit layz un mit nis. yakh hob dos alts

86
00:07:59,537 --> 00:08:06,784
az ir geshtupt tsukerlekh in moyl arayn bay di kristin, un ir gegebn finef hundert funt zi zol mikh lozn zitsn in kekh,

87
00:08:06,784 --> 00:08:14,308
un ikh hob oysgetsupt. zi iz geven eyn kind fun ale mit hor, mit tsep. ale zenen geven opgegolt in Otvotsk.

88
00:08:14,938 --> 00:08:19,964
un ikh bin dervayl, azoy vi ikh hob ir gehat bashtat bay keyn Otvotsk,

89
00:08:19,964 --> 00:08:25,716
bin ge- ongehoybn arbetn un yedn zuntik bin ikh geforn nor zen vayl m'hot nisht gearbet.

90
00:08:28,017 --> 00:08:32,280
in tsvishn tsayt, ven ikh hob gearbet in MINISTERSTWO,

91
00:08:32,556 --> 00:08:39,463
hot zikh geyavet eyner vos hot ibergelebt oykh oyfn oyfn poylishn oyfshtand un gevorn raykh.

92
00:08:39,463 --> 00:08:42,945
un er hot gekrign a voynung vu s'geven a shule.

93
00:08:43,356 --> 00:08:53,334
a a a a a shule tsu lernen. nor s'gevezn, s- ikh vil araynrukn poylishe verter keseyder, derfar kumt mir on shver.

94
00:08:51,507 --> 00:08:53,509
s'makht nisht, s'makht nisht.

95
00:08:53,334 --> 00:09:01,726
iz zog ikh iz iz geven a a a a hoyz vos iz gevezn ruinirt fun bombardirn. iz geven a shule.

96
00:09:01,783 --> 00:09:10,079
in di shule hot er gekrign a groyse klas, ikh veys er hot gemuzt lernen efsher fertsik fuftsik kinder, ikh veys vifl.

97
00:09:10,272 --> 00:09:16,813
un er er hot ibergelebt un a bruder un a bruder's a tokhter, un di froy hot nisht ibergelebt.

98
00:09:17,038 --> 00:09:22,562
un dos iz gevezn undzerer a guter fra- a khaver. fun undzer, in undzer GIL.

99
00:09:22,562 --> 00:09:25,942
nor m'nisht geven azoy spetsyel noent.

100
00:09:25,948 --> 00:09:31,629
un zayn fr- iz er hot gevoynt vayt fun undz oykhet. m'hot eyn mol bazukht vu er hot gevoynt dort in Varshe.

101
00:09:32,142 --> 00:09:36,298
un er er hot zikh zeyer tsu undz geklebt, nokhn geto dertsu.

102
00:09:36,298 --> 00:09:42,682
un flegt er aroyfkumen. hot er eyn mol genumen fun undz genumen di fotografye. a kleyne.

103
00:09:43,735 --> 00:09:52,453
hot er bay, er ho- vi azoy er hot dos oysbahaltn veys ikh nisht, tsuzamen mit di gelter un in oyfshtand dem poylishn, vos zey hobn ibergelebt, shreklekh ibergelebt.

104
00:09:52,847 --> 00:09:54,292
geblibn lebn.

105
00:09:54,383 --> 00:10:01,695
un get mir di fotografye. un dernokhn hot mayn shvogerl eyner vos iz gekumen mit Ander's Armey, du veyst dokh do iz geven,

106
00:10:01,695 --> 00:10:06,285
a yingerer bruder fun mayn man gemakht a gresere, nor a ikh vil es zi nisht vayzn

107
00:10:06,285 --> 00:10:08,923
vayl zi h- vil nisht hern fun keyn SHOAH.

108
00:10:09,182 --> 00:10:16,331
un ikh vil nisht vayzn vi zi hot oysgezen in geto. fun geto vu zi iz alt gevezn fir yor shoyn.

109
00:10:16,540 --> 00:10:23,689
iz do a kl- hob ikh a herlekhe ZDJECIE, nor ikh vil nisht mit ir onheybn. s'iz geven shver iz es haynt nokh shver.

110
00:10:23,695 --> 00:10:34,019
ikh hob nisht keyn shum hilf mit ir. nor vos zi mit mir gemuzt geyn in der bank arayn vayl ikh ze nisht untertsushraybn, un ikh ze nisht optsutseyln. un do darf ikh dokh gelt far farn shpitol geyn.

111
00:10:34,019 --> 00:10:38,592
farshteyst? derfar hob ikh a harts zikh mit ir bashteln, a toyve.

112
00:10:38,592 --> 00:10:46,774
nemt zi sh- shteyn un ir mashin lozt zi shteyn un nemt SPECIAL, kumt in bank arayn mir tsu helfn opnemen di por funt.

113
00:10:47,809 --> 00:10:56,595
OK undz ve'mir nisht, s- m- ir muzt es nisht vayzn dos bild, s'makht nisht. ikh volt aykh gevolt fregn vu hot ir getrofn ayer tsveytn man?

114
00:10:56,753 --> 00:10:58,656
a mayn tsveytn man?

115
00:10:58,656 --> 00:11:06,782
hob ikh getrofn, dos dertseyl ikh dokh, bay dem vos hot ibergelebt, bay dem khaver, un er hot gekrign aza a groys tsimer.

116
00:11:06,782 --> 00:11:09,234
un zayn bruder iz epes gezesn.

117
00:11:09,628 --> 00:11:18,532
der an elterer bruder, a raykher mentsh, er hot gehat ontuekhtser oyf a eksterer gas oyf Zhelne fun me- mener zakhn.

118
00:11:18,724 --> 00:11:23,623
ikh veys nisht far vos er hot er iz gezesn, un un m'hot im bafrayt,

119
00:11:23,623 --> 00:11:30,094
hot er bashlosn er makht aza mine bibke, dos iz geven a zuntik, ven ikh gevezn barn kind.

120
00:11:30,094 --> 00:11:31,947
un ikh bin gekumen shoyn shpet.

121
00:11:32,275 --> 00:11:39,491
un er hot farbe- yidn hobn zikh dokh gehaltn eyner dem andern, vifl m'hot gekent m- zi- m'hot dokh koym getrofn zikh tsunoyf getrofn.

122
00:11:39,632 --> 00:11:46,376
ikh kum shoyn shpet tsurik fun kind, fun Otvotsk, kumt er tsu, der Yakub,

123
00:11:46,652 --> 00:11:51,812
a neyn, ikh s'iz geven shoyn vayl ikh hob im sh- Yakubn shoyn gekent a por teg.

124
00:11:51,812 --> 00:11:57,328
un s'hot zikh in mir gelibt vider an ofitsir, er hot mikh nisht opgelozt, a bokher, BEDIYUK in mayn GIL.

125
00:11:57,587 --> 00:12:02,323
tsvey yor elter. un ikh hob a kind shoyn fun fun fun fun akht yor.

126
00:12:02,650 --> 00:12:06,930
fun zibn yor, akht yor. mit a a kavalir.

127
00:12:06,936 --> 00:12:13,072
a klal, bin ikh fun im a- un un ikh hob gehat a gekrign a shtub fun MINISTERSTWO oykhet, fun fun der regirung.

128
00:12:13,078 --> 00:12:22,100
bay a pr- bay a koleye, bay eyner f- oyf der ban vos er hot gearbet, un er hot nisht gelebt nor zi hot gehat dray tsimern, hob ikh gekrign a tsimer noent fun der arbet.

129
00:12:22,343 --> 00:12:24,246
fun vanet aroptsugeyn arbetn.

130
00:12:24,246 --> 00:12:33,153
di arbet iz geven oyf der Gove, oyf der Gove iz geven oykh der komitet, nor in hekhere numern, un oyf Inzhenyerski tsen. zakhn vos ikh darf nisht gedenk ikh.

131
00:12:34,577 --> 00:12:43,340
alzo, ikh ikh ikh ho- ikh hob mikh far- un nisht gevolt trefn mit dem BACHUR,

132
00:12:43,340 --> 00:12:54,923
er hot tsugeshtelt ale gute zakhn az s'zol kumen oyslender, hot er gehat a JOB f- in in der in in in fun der regirung. der BA- BACHUR.

133
00:12:55,148 --> 00:13:00,440
iz geshtanen oyfn tash, a kaylekhike tish hob ikh gehat bay di goye vu ikh hob gevoynt,

134
00:13:00,514 --> 00:13:08,068
ful ongeshtelt, fun konzervn, fun kavyar, fun alding, un di flign hobn gegesn un ikh bin nisht gekumen shlofn dort ahin.

135
00:13:08,091 --> 00:13:12,813
un bin geganen, un dortn tsu dem vos hot ibergelebt un er hot gekrign di shtub,

136
00:13:12,813 --> 00:13:16,919
hot ver s'ge- ver s'gekumene fun lager, ver s'nor gekumen fun vanet iz,

137
00:13:16,919 --> 00:13:21,578
hot oyfgehongen a laylekh, un er hot gesh- shtelt er, er hot yo gehat a bet, az nisht a bet,

138
00:13:21,578 --> 00:13:27,289
fun breter, un m'hot fortn geshlofn. s'geven aza a rizn zal. nor a ruinirter.

139
00:13:27,531 --> 00:13:32,641
alzo, ikh kum tsu forn fun kind vos ikh hob ir bazukht, un dortn in Otvotsk

140
00:13:32,641 --> 00:13:36,620
iz azoy vi azoy vi ikh bin nor ongekumen dos ershte mol bazukhn,

141
00:13:36,880 --> 00:13:42,493
get zikh in mir a heng on nokh a kind, nor opgeshoyrn, un zogt MAMUSIU, mame!

142
00:13:43,427 --> 00:13:49,127
iz vos ikh hob gebrengt dernokhn mayn kind, iz dos kind geven, az ikh hob gehat shoyn tsvey kinder.

143
00:13:49,127 --> 00:13:55,160
un az yene iz geven shoyn opgeshoyrn, zi iz geven frier fun mayn kind, un ikh hob gebrengt a kind mit tsep.

144
00:13:55,160 --> 00:13:59,857
on a on a nis, on a on on farshidene brudikeytn.

145
00:14:00,285 --> 00:14:05,901
alzo, un ikh kum tsurik un ikh zets zikh avek oyf a bank, zitsn oyf oyf oyf benk,

146
00:14:05,901 --> 00:14:13,593
mit sh- breter epes gemakht tishn oyf aza mine oyfn, nokh di aza shtikl bal nokh dem bafrayen fun dem bruder.

147
00:14:13,887 --> 00:14:18,018
zitst do ikh veys keygn iber ikh veys f- fir finef mentshn.

148
00:14:18,018 --> 00:14:24,405
un ikh zits nor eyne aleyn fun di zayt do, un er keygn iber mir. kumt tsu der Yakub,

149
00:14:24,405 --> 00:14:26,809
un Yakub iz nisht andersh gevezn

150
00:14:26,809 --> 00:14:33,351
vi az ikh bin geblibn lebn, a fakt, er hot, UNK er hot afilek mayn fotografye fun mayn kind gehat, un er

151
00:14:33,351 --> 00:14:38,010
er aleyn hot nisht gehat keyn kind. un zayn vayb iz geven a miese, Rutke iz geven a sheynkeyt.

152
00:14:38,010 --> 00:14:42,006
alzo, nisht andersh nor Rutke iz geblibn lebn far zaynet vegn.

153
00:14:42,006 --> 00:14:45,960
a guter mentsh iz er gevezn. a guter fakhman, a shnayder.

154
00:14:47,383 --> 00:14:51,984
HAIKAR, u- un zey hobn zey hobn ongezamlt a farmegn,

155
00:14:52,277 --> 00:14:56,180
dos hot geheysn sha- sh- shaber, dos heyst ganvenen.

156
00:14:56,180 --> 00:15:01,907
vos fun farshidene baheltenishn fun dos, vos zenen gekumen raykh, zey hobn ober gelebt raykh.

157
00:15:02,082 --> 00:15:08,727
nor keyner fun der familye iz nisht geblibn nor eyn tokhter fun dem bruder, a inteligente BACHURAH,

158
00:15:08,727 --> 00:15:13,213
un zi hot mikh lib gehat shoyn fun der ershter on, zi hot nisht gehat vos tsu tun mit mir.

159
00:15:13,388 --> 00:15:16,824
ober dos mol tsurik vi azoy s'iz geven ven ikh hob bakent mayn man.

160
00:15:17,488 --> 00:15:23,872
a klal, er kumt tsu, Yakub, un er zogt azoy. s'iz shoyn gornisht geblibn far dir. vos zol ikh dir makhn? ikh gey dir makhn, zogt er,

161
00:15:23,872 --> 00:15:27,163
a JAJECZNICA, a JAJECZNICEA heys a a gepreglt ey.

162
00:15:27,163 --> 00:15:36,115
zog ikh, makh a gepreglt ey. brengt er tsu a gepreglt ey mit a gopl, er flegt mir vashn un presn afile.

163
00:15:37,519 --> 00:15:46,169
HAIKAR, er get mir dem gopl. yakh nem a shtikl ey, un vil nemen broyt.

164
00:15:46,311 --> 00:15:50,169
keygn iber mir shtekt eyner azoy oys dem moyl, dos moyl.

165
00:15:50,209 --> 00:15:59,045
geb a kuk, ligt a por hent, herlekhe sheyne, a man, a blonder, enlekh tsu der Nikey nor a shenerer.

166
00:15:59,085 --> 00:16:02,150
ir zet dokh oyf der foto az er iz a sheyner man gevezn.

167
00:16:03,507 --> 00:16:11,097
un get mikh a khap oyf di hent azoy nakher azoy vi a vi vi ⟨yurke⟩, azoy vi gornisht, un get mikh a trog aroys fun hoyz aroys un heyst mikh onkushn.

168
00:16:11,127 --> 00:16:14,999
dos ershte az er iz hot mit mir geshen, mit gevald mamesh.

169
00:16:14,999 --> 00:16:20,829
un di ale khevre, zayne bakante, zogn, s'dokh Yakub's v- kale!

170
00:16:20,829 --> 00:16:24,553
zi geyt dokh er ge- er nemt dokh ir keyn Bitol, s'vet dokh ir zayn gut!

171
00:16:24,553 --> 00:16:29,347
vos Shlamik! Shloyme hobn zey gerufn Shlame. Shlamik, loz ir op!

172
00:16:29,347 --> 00:16:32,424
di bakante vos zenen gezesn. azoy hob ikh im bakent.

173
00:16:32,582 --> 00:16:34,668
er hot mikh shoyn mer nisht opgelozt,

174
00:16:34,995 --> 00:16:39,826
do vu m'hot gearbet iz gevezn glaykh mit dem trotuar, vu m'geyt,

175
00:16:39,826 --> 00:16:49,164
oyf parter. dort iz a mol gevezn dos di m- di minis- di di regirungs anshtalt fun fun di banen, fun farker.

176
00:16:49,373 --> 00:16:55,191
hot men dortn gearbet un s-m'hot gekokht azoy gut far far Byerutn, far dem prezident,

177
00:16:55,191 --> 00:17:00,599
un far di ministorn. azoy hob ikh gehat dos zelbe esn, un ikh hob badorfn zen

178
00:17:00,599 --> 00:17:06,625
ts- un un m'hot badorfn dortn on tsudatn, un on zhurnaln, un on faserner.

179
00:17:06,625 --> 00:17:11,506
un on a a dos m- tsu kenen mestn. vayl s'gornisht nokh gevezn.

180
00:17:11,714 --> 00:17:19,643
nor kaponen iz geven, zey hobn gebrengt fun Lodzh, vos s'nokh geven fun Lodzh vos di daytshn hobn ibergelozt, hobn zey opgebrengt keseyder kaponen farshidene

181
00:17:19,643 --> 00:17:24,635
zakhn. m'hot yedn un mir oykh gegebn. yede vokh hot men mir gegebn a kapon.

182
00:17:26,109 --> 00:17:31,861
un i- un ikh hob badorfn akhtung gebn oyf di sh- shikses oyf di ts- oyf di tsvelef vos hobn gearbet.

183
00:17:31,861 --> 00:17:37,957
un ikh hob gedorfn aleyn on a zhurnaln oder alding, fleg ikh shnaydn oyf di figurn yedn eynem.

184
00:17:37,988 --> 00:17:42,626
un s'nokh geven azelkhe komones, iz gut oysgekumen. nor azoy hob ikh geshnitn vifl s-

185
00:17:42,626 --> 00:17:47,009
az ikh hob nisht gehat in gantsn keyn zhurnaln, nisht gornisht, nisht keyn nisht keyn tsudatn,

186
00:17:47,116 --> 00:17:51,990
m'hot kneplekh aleyn ibertsien un makhn. gornisht iz geven. a hefker.

187
00:17:51,996 --> 00:17:57,947
alzo, ikh hob opgearbet azoy nokher, un der un m'hot oyf der gas gezen

188
00:17:58,594 --> 00:18:07,363
ver es geyt. s'geven azoy di fentster groyse, hekhere hekhere fentster vi dos iz geven, nor fun der erd, fun der gas.

189
00:18:08,027 --> 00:18:10,805
al- zogt zogn di shikses azoy.

190
00:18:11,166 --> 00:18:15,997
Rutetshka, UNK

191
00:18:15,997 --> 00:18:21,318
UNK.

192
00:18:21,443 --> 00:18:30,532
do dreyt zikh arum a tseratene kap- kapete un epes a man, ze nor ver dos iz. ikh geb a kuk, s'iz er.

193
00:18:30,623 --> 00:18:34,560
der Shlamik. iz er geshtanen, er hot mikh gehitn in MINISTERSTWO,

194
00:18:34,560 --> 00:18:39,088
ikh hob im shoyn nisht gekent optretn, azoy iz es gevorn derfun.

195
00:18:38,520 --> 00:18:41,343
un ven hot ets gehayratet?

196
00:18:40,195 --> 00:18:41,855
demolt bald.

197
00:18:41,343 --> 00:18:42,362
bald.

198
00:18:42,553 --> 00:18:45,888
un ven hot ets farlozt Poyln? vi lang zent ets,

199
00:18:47,160 --> 00:18:50,309
m'iz gevorn bafrayt in finef un fertsikstn yor.

200
00:18:51,042 --> 00:18:58,680
ongehoybn arbetn hob ikh, ikh farshtey az s'iz shoyn gevezn,

201
00:19:00,627 --> 00:19:05,261
ikh ikh veys a tsvey monatn hot gedoyert, mitn lign in shpitol, mit alding.

202
00:19:07,039 --> 00:19:13,091
un undz un un dernokh hot ongerukt a zumer, alts iz tsvey un fertsikster yor,

203
00:19:13,958 --> 00:19:22,805
f- finef un fertsikstn yor, hot men khasene gehat. un er hot ongehoybn handlen.

204
00:19:22,805 --> 00:19:26,155
yo, a klal, azoy vi ikh hob gezen er ken zikh nisht optshepen,

205
00:19:26,155 --> 00:19:34,235
un vegn a- als men iz er geven tsum gefeln. un keyn soydes hob ikh nisht gevust, ikh hob nisht gezen er hot andere khesroynes,

206
00:19:34,309 --> 00:19:37,149
alzo s'ge- hot er mikh gehitn.

207
00:19:37,149 --> 00:19:45,156
un der Yakub iz gekumen er hot gehat tsugegreyt fir fir tsimern in Biton, mit a klavir mit alding farn kind iz geven greyt.

208
00:19:45,156 --> 00:19:47,398
un er hot gevust az er hot nisht keyn gelt.

209
00:19:47,404 --> 00:19:52,143
iz Yakubn im gezogt, Shlamik, ikh veys dokh az du host nisht keyn gelt un host lib

210
00:19:52,143 --> 00:19:55,583
a a a g- a a shnepsl, un host lib a portn,

211
00:19:55,690 --> 00:20:00,471
na dir hundert toyznt zlotes, un loz ir op, Rutke, vos vilstu fun ir?

212
00:20:00,471 --> 00:20:08,475
vi vestu ir gebn tsu dos vos ir kind darf? er hot im opgeredt un er hot im gevolt iberkoyfn. zogt er, Rutke vet zayn mayn mayn froy.

213
00:20:09,578 --> 00:20:14,080
azoy iz gevorn. nor PITOM, get a kum,

214
00:20:14,080 --> 00:20:19,986
yo, ikh hob gearbet in MINISTERSTWO, s'nokh nisht geven keyn post, s'nokh nisht geganen keyn shum farbindung mit oysland.

215
00:20:19,986 --> 00:20:28,331
iz geforn a a a a shishke a MINISTROWA, der minister, a ⟨grar⟩ minister mit der froy,

216
00:20:28,331 --> 00:20:30,550
hob ikh ir gebetn, keyn Kanade.

217
00:20:30,550 --> 00:20:33,905
hob ikh ir gebetn, ikh hob gehat dem adres fun mayn bruder,

218
00:20:34,333 --> 00:20:40,287
az vu dos iz, afilek yetst gedenk ikh, volt ikh gekent zogn.

219
00:20:40,287 --> 00:20:46,505
hob ikh ir gebetn zi zol araynvarfn a briv, er iz in Kuba, in Havana,

220
00:20:46,505 --> 00:20:52,969
un s'iz der un der nomen, vayl ikh hob dokh s- vi ver veyst ven do vet zayn a komunikatsye?

221
00:20:52,969 --> 00:20:57,744
un un un z- un mit a briv un ikh hob im geshribn,

222
00:20:57,744 --> 00:21:00,550
ikh bin aleyn, dos kind iz mir geblibn lebn.

223
00:21:02,025 --> 00:21:07,093
azoy vi azoy vi zi iz gekumen keyn Kanade hot zi arayngevorfn dem briv,

224
00:21:07,093 --> 00:21:12,043
ikh hob gekrign an entfer oyf di, ikh hob dokh gehat an adres, gevoynt bay di koleyarke,

225
00:21:12,100 --> 00:21:17,392
iz gekumen an adres, shvester, ikh tu shoyn ikh zol dikh nemen ariber mitn kind.

226
00:21:17,365 --> 00:21:18,607
keyn Kuba.

227
00:21:18,158 --> 00:21:19,907
key- yo, keyn Kuba.

228
00:21:19,170 --> 00:21:22,792
un fun der resht fun der mishpokhe, iz keyner nisht tsurikgekumen?

229
00:21:22,866 --> 00:21:28,395
k- fun der mishpokhe keyner nisht. ale zenen nokh farn kesl tsugenumen gevorn.

230
00:21:28,485 --> 00:21:33,558
farn ke- vayl ale hobn gevoynt in yenem gegnt vu s'iz geven der umshlag-plats, ikh oykhet.

231
00:21:33,835 --> 00:21:39,803
di letste gas far a poylishe gas iz geven mayn gas vu ikh hob gevoynt, oyf Shishlive.

232
00:21:40,618 --> 00:21:44,459
hot der bruder geshribn az er vil aykh brengen nemen keyn Kuba.

233
00:21:44,365 --> 00:21:47,886
y- yo, tsi ikh vil? ikh hob dokh geshribn az ikh bin geblibn.

234
00:21:46,828 --> 00:21:53,370
neyn neyn, er hot geshribn az er vil aykh breng- nemen keyn Kuba vi s'iz vi a bald ven s'vet zayn meglekh.

235
00:21:53,258 --> 00:21:58,511
neyn, nisht in ven s'vet zayn meglekh, er er er makht shoyn er zol epes tun.

236
00:21:57,662 --> 00:21:58,601
KEN.

237
00:21:58,511 --> 00:22:07,021
er un ikh hob gekrign dem entfer, bin ikh gegangen eyn mol bloyz keyn dos, nor er hot mikh dervayl gehitn, mayn man, der der Shlamik.

238
00:22:07,197 --> 00:22:20,151
a klal, ikh ikh ikh zog im az er shraybt er redt makhn az undz tsu forn. zogt er, vu bin ikh? zog ikh, du kumst nisht in batrakht. tsu mayn bruder for ikh aleyn, ikh hob nisht khasene mit Yakubn oykhet nisht.

239
00:22:20,494 --> 00:22:23,739
un iz iz dos dos muz es zayn.

240
00:22:23,739 --> 00:22:29,911
zogt er, oyb azoy, lomir bikhlal farlozn Poyln, farlozn di arbet.

241
00:22:29,911 --> 00:22:33,230
ikh hob on a derloybenish zikh bafrayt, vayl ikh hob gehert in a gev-

242
00:22:33,230 --> 00:22:36,528
in a ekstere opteylung fun dray hundert un zibetsn mentshn

243
00:22:36,528 --> 00:22:41,025
vos m'hot badorfn hitn di konter-revolutsyonern. farhstey-

244
00:22:41,301 --> 00:22:49,406
azoy az ikh hob oyfgegebn oykhet az mayn tateshi iz gevezn, ikh hob shoyn dakht zikh geredt vegn dem mit dir vegn, ikh gedenk nisht.

245
00:22:49,406 --> 00:22:52,517
HAIKAR, ober yetst iz dokh vikhtik vos ikh zog.

246
00:22:54,683 --> 00:23:01,835
hob ikh im gezogt oyb iz iz hot er ongehoybn handlen, ongehoybn fardinen ekstere,

247
00:23:01,835 --> 00:23:08,076
un m'hot nisht gevoynt shoyn mer in Prage nor in Valbzhikh, in a farnumene gebitn vos hobn a mol gevezn daytshn,

248
00:23:08,183 --> 00:23:15,444
un in in un in Breslau iz geven a gants lebn. eyns hobn zikh di daytshn dortn

249
00:23:15,444 --> 00:23:21,114
zeks vokhn nokh geshlogn ven Berlin iz shoyn geven genumen, iz di shtot gevezn hefker,

250
00:23:21,114 --> 00:23:26,075
un di shto- un tse- un tsevorfn, un un un f- un ruinirt,

251
00:23:26,075 --> 00:23:29,756
nor yidn vos zenen ongekumen fun Poyln un fun un fun Rusland

252
00:23:29,756 --> 00:23:35,112
zenen ge- hobn dortn gevoynt in Breslau. hot gevoynt dort a a a a rebetsn oykhet,

253
00:23:35,112 --> 00:23:40,041
hot zi oysgearbet toyznt zibn hundert un fuftsik yidn aroystsufirn als

254
00:23:40,041 --> 00:23:45,829
daytshishe yidn, un hot genumen fun yedn eynem hundert un finef un tsvontsik dolar.

255
00:23:45,829 --> 00:23:50,021
zogt er, un un un undz ho'mir gevoynt nokh a bisl vayter in Valbzhikh,

256
00:23:50,079 --> 00:23:53,441
zol men, un mayne a CHAVERA hot gevoynt in Breslau.

257
00:23:53,441 --> 00:23:59,105
ze'mir geforn arayngeforn keyn Breslau, un m'hot alts gekoyft dires, nisht gekrign.

258
00:23:59,247 --> 00:24:02,610
herlekhe dires ibergelozt mit farshidene zakhn.

259
00:24:02,610 --> 00:24:11,812
alzo ze'mir arayngeforn, un m'hot batsolt far far ale dray oyf falshe nemen oyf tsu forn keyn Daytshland.

260
00:24:13,152 --> 00:24:19,997
dos iz gevezn alding nokh in finef un fertsikstn, in s'shoyn dos iz shoyn geven in zeks un fertsikstn yor.

261
00:24:21,927 --> 00:24:29,396
m'hot m'iz aroysgeforn zibetsn hundert un fu- un fuftsik yidn, tsi vifl s'iz nokh geven, efsher a por un fuftsik,

262
00:24:29,419 --> 00:24:33,069
iz gevezn punkt a tog ven m'hot badorfn shtimen

263
00:24:33,069 --> 00:24:37,412
yo far der regirung, nisht far der regirung. TAK, NIE, yo, neyn.

264
00:24:37,435 --> 00:24:42,120
ho'mir gezdonzhet optsushtimen, un far nakhts ze'mir avekgeforn ale.

265
00:24:42,936 --> 00:24:50,096
oyfn veg iz geven a gantse dos, in TOWAROWA, in in nisht in keyn normal banen.

266
00:24:50,096 --> 00:24:57,577
nor vos m'firt ki, dos heyst handls, TOWAROWA vagonen.

267
00:24:57,280 --> 00:24:59,214
transport-vagonen.

268
00:24:58,377 --> 00:25:07,584
in transport-vagonen. ze'mir gezes- ze'mir azoy opgelegn, bin ikh azoy opgelegn oyf a bisl dos shtroy, ale,

269
00:25:07,675 --> 00:25:13,234
un dernokhn iz arayngekumen a kontrolir, shpeter shoyn, m'iz shoyn geven nisht nisht in Poyln, nor oyf der

270
00:25:13,235 --> 00:25:15,576
oyf anderer zayn fun Daytshland,

271
00:25:15,576 --> 00:25:21,363
iz gekumen a kontrolir, un far- un yedn gefregt vi er heyst. yeder iz geforn oyfn an ander nomen.

272
00:25:21,363 --> 00:25:25,955
hot mayn man hot gezogt, ikh hob gezogt Kurts,

273
00:25:25,955 --> 00:25:30,680
un mayn man hot er oykh gezogt Kurts. zogt er der zogt der kontrolir oyf doytsh,

274
00:25:30,720 --> 00:25:34,592
er hot dos gut gut gelernt. er hot gevust, er iz geven opgekoyft

275
00:25:34,592 --> 00:25:39,401
az dos forn falshe yi- ikh bin epes geforn epes far Klara Kurts.

276
00:25:39,788 --> 00:25:44,282
ikh veys nisht far, oyf a falshn nomen. ale zenen azoy geforn, ale hundert un fuftsi-

277
00:25:44,282 --> 00:25:51,555
HAIKAR, nokh dem, iz gekumen oykhet a, iz geforn mit undz eyner tsurik vos iz bafrayt gevorn in Bergn-Belzn,

278
00:25:51,555 --> 00:25:57,340
a khaver hot er gebrengt tsurik keyn Poyln, hot men ir oykhet mitgenumen fun Breslau,

279
00:25:57,387 --> 00:26:02,663
iz men un zi hot gevust vegn Bergn-Belzn. ze'mir farforn keyn Bergn-Belzn

280
00:26:02,663 --> 00:26:06,706
m'iz ongekumen in tsvelftn LIPIEC keyn Bergn-Belzn,

281
00:26:06,889 --> 00:26:12,092
iz eyner hot glaykh tsugekumen un gezogt, ikh ken dikh fun Varshe, tsu mayn man.

282
00:26:12,092 --> 00:26:18,510
un undz ho'mir gefirt a valizke mit gelt oykhet, vos iz dort nisht geganen, un in Daytshland iz es gut geven, markn.

283
00:26:18,955 --> 00:26:24,326
un khuts dem gelt oykhet, un afilek tsirung vos m'hot gebakn ekstere ayn

284
00:26:24,326 --> 00:26:30,317
un m'hot get- in di khales un alding, azoy az m'iz gekumen nisht orem keyn Daytshland.

285
00:26:30,317 --> 00:26:34,527
iz gege- un ikh bin gevezn krank, ikh hob gehaltn in eyn blutikn,

286
00:26:34,527 --> 00:26:40,526
hot men mikh genumen koydemen hot men mikh aroyfgegebn oyf a blok tsu di po- vu di politsey hot gevoynt,

287
00:26:40,526 --> 00:26:45,391
un lerers un s'geven a klinik un s'geven a studye alts in dem blok.

288
00:26:46,377 --> 00:26:49,491
un vi zi kumt take zogt take zi veyst vegn demer,

289
00:26:49,491 --> 00:26:53,406
vayl zi iz oykhet bafrayt gevorn in Bergn-Belzn, zi iz nokh geblibn nokh vayter.

290
00:26:53,406 --> 00:26:57,534
zi hot gelernt nokh in gimnazye di vos zi kumt tsu mir, fun Amkha.

291
00:26:57,565 --> 00:27:01,440
HAIK- HAIKAR un dos kind iz geganen arayn in shule arayn.

292
00:27:01,142 --> 00:27:02,840
in Bergn-Belzn?

293
00:27:01,918 --> 00:27:03,869
in Be- in Bergn-Belzn.

294
00:27:03,943 --> 00:27:09,413
iz zi iz gegangen in a shule normal, ikh veys in driter klas, ikh veys dort UNK hot gekent zayn.

295
00:27:09,413 --> 00:27:13,604
un zi zogt az zi iz shoyn gegangen in in gimnazye. s'geven a gimnazye oykhet.

296
00:27:13,660 --> 00:27:17,572
un mir hot men gegebn, ikh hob gevizn az ikh for keyn Kuba.

297
00:27:18,270 --> 00:27:22,820
hot men mir oysnamlekh oysgezukht aza tsimer azoy groys vi mayn kokh.

298
00:27:23,232 --> 00:27:27,998
un zey hobn gornisht gekrign. s'geforn azoy, nokh a CHAVERA mayne, vos zi

299
00:27:27,998 --> 00:27:33,260
zi iz dernokh fun danet shoyn geforn avek keyn Oystarlye, hot zi geshvangert,

300
00:27:33,260 --> 00:27:42,243
un ir vos m'hot zi hot getrofn az er volt gevorn ayngezetst fun di bol- fun di bolshevikes, vayl er iz geven der MENAHEL fun a garazh,

301
00:27:42,840 --> 00:27:50,692
az er volt gegan avek tsu di vayse bern, zogt er, vos voltstu getun, bist gekumen, zogt er, tsurik? un zi iz shoyn, zi hot in dray tog arum geboyrn a kind.

302
00:27:50,692 --> 00:27:53,536
nor di shtub hob ikh bakumen, eyn shtikl shtibl.

303
00:27:53,536 --> 00:27:57,662
iz undz ze'mir geshlofn oyf der erd, un tsvey ayzerne betlekh iz gevezn,

304
00:27:57,662 --> 00:28:02,944
alzo, ikh hob gek- zi hot geboyrn, eyne hot geboyrn bald, iz zi aroys, hot zi gekrign a

305
00:28:02,944 --> 00:28:09,902
a a a shtub a di ergets, ikh bin nisht keyn mol geven dortn, un er hot ongehoybn arbetn in der politsey.

306
00:28:11,342 --> 00:28:17,883
un di tsveyte iz nokh geblibn mit mir un hot oykh geshvangert, un zi hot gevolt poter vern fun dem man, zi hot im nisht lib gehat.

307
00:28:17,957 --> 00:28:23,182
zi hot gehat zeyer fil derfolg. zi iz geven azelkhe vos hot gehat a seks-apil, ekstere.

308
00:28:23,205 --> 00:28:27,721
nisht keyn sheynkeyt, nor a seks-apil. mener hobn ir nor ongekukt, zenen zey geven fertik.

309
00:28:27,829 --> 00:28:33,015
hot zi im gevolt patern, un zi iz shoyn geven oykh efsher in, iz oyb zi hot geboyrn in yanuar,

310
00:28:33,015 --> 00:28:36,648
iz vifl geven in in LIPIEC? ikh, epes a por monatn.

311
00:28:36,807 --> 00:28:44,951
flegt zi shpringen, az di b- di a POCIAG di di ban iz geblibn shteyn, flegn zi mit mayn tokhter shpringen fun di dekher az s'zol ir kalye vern.

312
00:28:45,042 --> 00:28:49,468
un mikh hot men dervayl genumen in shpitol arayn, un s'hot zikh azoy fartsoygn a por vokhn.

313
00:28:49,468 --> 00:28:54,616
a klal, vi ikh kum eyn mol tsu geyn, ikh bin ge- mikh gefilt a bisl beser, ⟨m'hot gegebn zikh a ZASIEGes⟩,

314
00:28:54,616 --> 00:28:58,340
hob ikh bin ikh epes oyf a tog aheymkumen. ikh kum ahey- aheym,

315
00:28:58,403 --> 00:29:01,893
di shtub iz dokh geven a shtikl an ayzern betl mit gornisht,

316
00:29:02,018 --> 00:29:06,855
nor ikh bin dokh gekumen fun shpitol un aheym tsum kind un un tsu mayn man,

317
00:29:07,030 --> 00:29:11,057
zo- z- geyt zi aroys mitn, zi hot nokh oykhet gevoynt,

318
00:29:11,097 --> 00:29:14,384
geyt zi aroys es mit a pekele. zog ikh Stefa,

319
00:29:14,384 --> 00:29:19,494
UNK RAK poylish. Ste- Stefa, vu geystu?

320
00:29:20,074 --> 00:29:25,468
zogt zi, zest dokh vu ikh gey. veyst dokh in vosere shtand ikh bin, un far vos ikh bin geshprungen fun di dekher.

321
00:29:25,677 --> 00:29:28,337
zog ikh, kuk oyf mir, zog ikh.

322
00:29:28,461 --> 00:29:32,741
vi krank ikh bin vos ikh hob oykh nisht gevolt hobn keyn kind, un ikh hob oykh gevolt.

323
00:29:33,068 --> 00:29:38,884
ikh hob ir koym opgeredt un ayngeredt zi zol geyn tsurik. zi iz geganen kalye makhn dos kind.

324
00:29:38,974 --> 00:29:43,679
a sof iz zi hot zi gelebt in yanuar un zi iz nokh shpeter gekumen do in land arayn.

325
00:29:43,679 --> 00:29:49,717
un hot geboyrn in fiftstn yanuar iz zibn un fertsik,

326
00:29:49,723 --> 00:29:56,166
hot zi geboyrn a kind, a meydele, un hot gekrign a voynung. azoy ikh hob shoyn gehat di voynung biz tsum avekforn,

327
00:29:56,166 --> 00:30:05,580
bin aroysgeforn punkt in zelbn tog vos ikh bin gekumen tsum yor, mit der tsveyter TURE fun di legale men- fun di le- fun di tsen toyznt sertifikatn,

328
00:30:05,822 --> 00:30:09,893
un er hor ir ge- m'hot batsolt gut derfar, ze'mir gekumen in land arayn.

329
00:30:09,940 --> 00:30:12,046
undz e'mir vayter oyf der nekhster kasete.

